<parameter name="content"># ZAMSTATE Real Estate Platform - Project Proposal

## Executive Summary

**ZAMSTATE** is a comprehensive real estate management platform built with the MERN stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js) designed specifically for the Zambian property market. The platform enables property owners, tenants, agents, and investors to manage properties, bookings, maintenance requests, and communications all in one place.

