## Project Overview

### What is ZAMSTATE?

ZAMSTATE is a web-based real estate management platform that connects:
- **Property Owners** - Manage listings, view bookings, track payments
- **Tenants** - Search properties, book viewings, report maintenance
- **Agents** - List properties, schedule viewings, close deals
- **Investors** - Browse opportunities, track investments
- **Admins** - Platform management, analytics, user moderation

### Why Zambia?

- Growing real estate market in Lusaka and major cities
- Limited digital property management solutions
- High mobile phone penetration
- Increasing internet connectivity

---

## Problem Statement

### Current Challenges

1. **Manual Property Management**
   - Property owners use spreadsheets and WhatsApp groups
   - No centralized system for tracking multiple properties

2. **Inefficient Tenant Communication**
   - Scattered communication across phone calls, SMS, WhatsApp
   - No audit trail of maintenance requests

3. **Booking Chaos**
   - Double-bookings due to lack of centralized calendar
   - No automated reminders or confirmations

4. **Payment Tracking Issues**
   - Cash-based transactions with no digital records
   - Difficulty tracking rent payments and outstanding balances

5. **Maintenance Disorganization**
   - Lost maintenance requests
   - No status tracking or accountability

---

## Objectives

### Primary Objectives

| Objective | Key Result | Success Metric |
|-----------|------------|----------------|
| Centralize property management | Single platform for all operations | 500+ properties listed |
| Digitize tenant communication | Reduce phone calls by 60% | 1000+ messages/month |
| Automate booking process | Eliminate double-bookings | 0 conflicts |
| Enable digital payments | 50% of transactions digital | 500+ payments processed |
| Streamline maintenance | 80% issues resolved in 48h | <48hr resolution time |

### Secondary Objectives

- Generate analytics reports for property owners
- Enable property comparison and search filters
- Build investor dashboard for portfolio tracking
- Create mobile-responsive experience

---

## Features & Functionalities

### Core Features

#### 1. Authentication & Authorization
- [ ] User registration with role selection
- [ ] JWT-based authentication
- [ ] Role-based access control (RBAC)
- [ ] Password reset via email
- [ ] Email verification

#### 2. Property Management
- [ ] CRUD operations for properties
- [ ] Image upload with Cloudinary
- [ ] Video tour support
- [ ] Floor plans
- [ ] Property features (bedrooms, bathrooms, parking, etc.)
- [ ] Location mapping with coordinates
- [ ] Property status (available, rented, sold, maintenance)

#### 3. Search & Discovery
- [ ] Advanced search filters
  - Property type
  - Price range
  - Location (city, township)
  - Number of bedrooms/bathrooms
  - Amenities
- [ ] Search by map
- [ ] Save favorite properties
- [ ] Property comparison

#### 4. Booking System
- [ ] Schedule property viewings
- [ ] Booking status workflow
  - Pending → Confirmed → Completed/Cancelled
- [ ] Calendar view for property owners
- [ ] Automated email/SMS confirmations
- [ ] Booking history

#### 5. Messaging System
- [ ] Real-time chat using Socket.io
- [ ] Conversation threads
- [ ] File/image attachments
- [ ] Message read receipts
- [ ] Notification system

#### 6. Maintenance Tracking
- [ ] Submit maintenance requests
- [ ] Upload issue images
- [ ] Priority levels (low, medium, high, urgent)
- [ ] Status tracking (pending, in_progress, completed)
- [ ] Cost tracking
- [ ] Assignment to service providers

#### 7. Payment System
- [ ] Rent payment tracking
- [ ] Deposit management
- [ ] Payment history
- [ ] Generate receipts
- [ ] Integration with mobile money (MTN, Airtel)

#### 8. Analytics Dashboard
- [ ] Property performance metrics
- [ ] Revenue tracking
- [ ] Occupancy rates
- [ ] Maintenance costs
- [ ] Booking statistics
- [ ] Export reports (PDF, Excel)

