## User Roles & Permissions

### Role Matrix

| Feature | Tenant | Owner | Agent | Admin |
|---------|--------|-------|-------|-------|
| View properties | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Create listing | ❌ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Edit own listing | ❌ | ✅ (own) | ✅ (own) | ✅ |
| Book property | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ |
| Manage bookings | ❌ | ✅ (own) | ✅ (assigned) | ✅ |
| Send messages | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Create maintenance | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Resolve maintenance | ❌ | ✅ (own) | ✅ | ✅ |
| View analytics | ❌ | ✅ (own) | ✅ | ✅ |
| Manage users | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |
| Platform settings | ❌ | ❌ | ❌ | ✅ |

