## Budget Estimate

### Development Costs

| Item | Cost (ZMW) | Cost (USD) |
|------|------------|------------|
| Frontend Development | 80,000 | $3,200 |
| Backend Development | 80,000 | $3,200 |
| Database Design | 20,000 | $800 |
| UI/UX Design | 30,000 | $1,200 |
| Testing & QA | 25,000 | $1,000 |
| **Subtotal** | **235,000** | **$9,400** |

### Infrastructure Costs (Monthly)

| Service | Cost (ZMW) | Cost (USD) |
|---------|------------|------------|
| MongoDB Atlas (M10) | 1,500 | $60 |
| Cloudinary (Pro) | 800 | $32 |
| Vercel/Netlify | 500 | $20 |
| Domain (.zm) | 300 | $12 |
| SSL Certificate | 200 | $8 |
| **Subtotal (Monthly)** | **3,300** | **$132** |

### Optional Add-ons

| Item | Cost (ZMW) | Cost (USD) |
|------|------------|------------|
| Mobile App (React Native) | 150,000 | $6,000 |
| SMS Integration | 2,000/mo | $80/mo |
| Email Service (SendGrid) | 500/mo | $20/mo |
| Google Maps API | 1,000/mo | $40/mo |

### Total Initial Investment

| Category | Cost (ZMW) | Cost (USD) |
|----------|------------|------------|
| Development | 235,000 | $9,400 |
| Year 1 Infrastructure | 39,600 | $1,584 |
| Contingency (10%) | 27,460 | $1,098 |
| **Total** | **302,060** | **$12,082** |

