## Risks & Mitigation

| Risk | Impact | Probability | Mitigation Strategy |
|------|--------|-------------|-------------------|
| Scope creep | High | High | Clear requirements, change management process |
| Performance issues | Medium | Medium | Load testing, caching, CDN |
| Security vulnerabilities | High | Medium | Regular audits, OWASP compliance |
| User adoption | High | High | User research, training, support |
| Technical debt | Medium | Medium | Code reviews, refactoring sprints |
| Vendor lock-in | Low | Low | Use open-source technologies |
| Data loss | High | Low | Regular backups, disaster recovery |

